---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="Meet the Team - Cloud Intelligence Leadership & Experts"
  description="Meet the elite team behind Cloud Intelligence, led by CEO James Burgess (GCP Certified Lead Architect) and COO Kaitlyn Wilson. 8 professionals dedicated to software excellence."
  keywords="Cloud Intelligence team, James Burgess CEO, Kaitlyn Wilson COO, software engineering team, GCP certified, Cape Town developers"
  showNavbar={true}
>
  <main class="team-page">
    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <section class="team-hero">
      <div class="container">
        <h1>Meet Our Team</h1>
        <p class="hero-subtitle">Elite professionals dedicated to software engineering excellence</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Leadership Team -->
    <section class="leadership-team">
      <div class="container">
        <h2>Leadership</h2>
        <div class="leadership-grid">
          <!-- James Burgess -->
          <div class="team-member featured">
            <div class="member-image">
              <img src="/webtest/team/james-burgess.jpg" alt="James Burgess, CEO and Lead Architect" onerror="this.style.display='none'; this.nextElementSibling.style.display='flex'">
              <div class="image-placeholder">JB</div>
            </div>
            <div class="member-info">
              <h3>James Burgess</h3>
              <p class="role">CEO & Lead Architect</p>
              <p class="credentials">GCP Cloud Engineer Certified</p>
              
              <div class="bio">
                <p>James is the visionary architect behind Cloud Intelligence's success. A true builder by heart, he combines deep technical expertise with an artisan's approach to software development. His exceptional ability to understand complex systems and break them into elegant, manageable components has been instrumental in delivering transformative solutions for enterprise clients.</p>
                
                <p>With his GCP Cloud Engineer certification and years of experience in enterprise architecture, James leads our technical strategy and ensures every project meets our uncompromising quality standards. His philosophy of treating software development as an art form permeates throughout our entire organization.</p>
              </div>

              <div class="expertise">
                <h4>Key Expertise</h4>
                <ul>
                  <li>Enterprise Systems Architecture</li>
                  <li>Cloud-Native Solutions (GCP Certified)</li>
                  <li>Complex Data Pipeline Design</li>
                  <li>AI/ML Integration & Implementation</li>
                  <li>Team Leadership & Strategic Vision</li>
                </ul>
              </div>

              <div class="achievements">
                <h4>Notable Achievements</h4>
                <ul>
                  <li>Led development of healthcare platform processing $400M+ in transactions</li>
                  <li>Architected systems serving 1M+ users across 100+ countries</li>
                  <li>Designed ETL pipelines processing 8TB+ daily data volumes</li>
                  <li>Built award-winning AI-powered document processing systems</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Kaitlyn Wilson -->
          <div class="team-member featured">
            <div class="member-image">
              <img src="/webtest/team/kaitlyn-wilson.jpg" alt="Kaitlyn Wilson, COO" onerror="this.style.display='none'; this.nextElementSibling.style.display='flex'">
              <div class="image-placeholder">KW</div>
            </div>
            <div class="member-info">
              <h3>Kaitlyn Wilson</h3>
              <p class="role">Chief Operating Officer</p>
              <p class="credentials">Operations & Strategy Leader</p>
              
              <div class="bio">
                <p>Kaitlyn is the operational backbone of Cloud Intelligence, ensuring our boutique approach scales effectively while maintaining our commitment to excellence. As co-founder and COO, she brings strategic vision and operational expertise that enables our team to deliver consistent value to enterprise clients.</p>
                
                <p>Her focus on process optimization, team development, and client success has been crucial in building Cloud Intelligence's reputation as a premium software engineering partner. Kaitlyn's leadership ensures our remote-first culture thrives while maintaining the highest standards of professionalism.</p>
              </div>

              <div class="expertise">
                <h4>Key Expertise</h4>
                <ul>
                  <li>Strategic Operations Management</li>
                  <li>Remote Team Leadership</li>
                  <li>Client Relationship Management</li>
                  <li>Business Process Optimization</li>
                  <li>Quality Assurance & Standards</li>
                </ul>
              </div>

              <div class="achievements">
                <h4>Notable Achievements</h4>
                <ul>
                  <li>Co-founded Cloud Intelligence and scaled to 8-person elite team</li>
                  <li>Established partnerships with international enterprise clients</li>
                  <li>Implemented quality processes achieving zero security incidents</li>
                  <li>Built remote-first culture with 100% client satisfaction rate</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Core Team -->
    <section class="core-team">
      <div class="container">
        <h2>Our Core Team</h2>
        <p class="team-intro">Our carefully curated team of 8 elite professionals represents the cream of the crop in their respective disciplines. Each member brings exceptional skills, unwavering dedication, and a shared commitment to delivering nothing short of perfection.</p>
        
        <div class="team-structure">
          <div class="team-category">
            <h3>Engineering Team</h3>
            <p>4+ Senior Engineers led by James, specializing in:</p>
            <ul>
              <li>Full-stack development (Django, Vue.js, React)</li>
              <li>Data engineering and ETL pipeline development</li>
              <li>Cloud infrastructure and Kubernetes orchestration</li>
              <li>AI/ML integration and context engineering</li>
              <li>Enterprise security and compliance implementation</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="team-category">
            <h3>Design & Product</h3>
            <p>1 Senior Designer focusing on:</p>
            <ul>
              <li>User experience (UX) design and research</li>
              <li>User interface (UI) design and prototyping</li>
              <li>Brand identity and visual design systems</li>
              <li>Mobile-first responsive design</li>
              <li>Accessibility and inclusive design practices</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="team-category">
            <h3>Product Management</h3>
            <p>1 Senior Product Manager responsible for:</p>
            <ul>
              <li>Product strategy and roadmap development</li>
              <li>Client requirements analysis and documentation</li>
              <li>Cross-functional team coordination</li>
              <li>Quality assurance and testing oversight</li>
              <li>Project delivery and client communication</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="team-category">
            <h3>Business Intelligence</h3>
            <p>1 Skilled BI Analyst creating:</p>
            <ul>
              <li>Advanced dashboard development with Metabase</li>
              <li>Data visualization and reporting solutions</li>
              <li>Business analytics and insights generation</li>
              <li>Public data analysis and research projects</li>
              <li>Client-specific intelligence solutions</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Team Culture -->
    <section class="team-culture">
      <div class="container">
        <h2>Our Culture</h2>
        <div class="culture-grid">
          <div class="culture-item">
            <h4>Remote-First Excellence</h4>
            <p>We've mastered the art of remote collaboration, enabling us to work with the best talent regardless of location while maintaining our Cape Town roots.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="culture-item">
            <h4>Craftsman Philosophy</h4>
            <p>Every team member shares our deep love and appreciation for the art of building with software, treating each project as a masterpiece.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="culture-item">
            <h4>Continuous Learning</h4>
            <p>Our team stays at the forefront of technology, continuously expanding expertise in AI, cloud technologies, and emerging development practices.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="culture-item">
            <h4>Quality Obsession</h4>
            <p>We maintain uncompromising quality standards, ensuring every deliverable reflects our commitment to excellence and correctness.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Join Our Team -->
    <section class="join-team">
      <div class="container">
        <h2>Join Our Elite Team</h2>
        <p>We're always looking for exceptional talent who share our passion for software craftsmanship and commitment to excellence. While we maintain our core team of 8 professionals, we expand strategically by adding specialists as new clients require.</p>
        
        <div class="hiring-approach">
          <h3>Our Hiring Philosophy</h3>
          <p>We believe in <strong>demand-based expansion</strong>, leveraging James's reliable network of elite developers and using OfferZen as our secondary hiring channel. When we do hire, we look for:</p>
          
          <ul class="hiring-criteria">
            <li>Exceptional technical skills and proven expertise</li>
            <li>Commitment to quality and attention to detail</li>
            <li>Ability to work independently in a remote environment</li>
            <li>Passion for continuous learning and improvement</li>
            <li>Alignment with our values of correctness and craftsmanship</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="contact-hiring">
          <p>If you're an elite developer who shares our vision and values, we'd love to hear from you.</p>
          <a href="/book-a-call" class="cta-button">Get in Touch</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</Layout>

<style lang="scss">
